00:34:59.520 --> 00:35:06.159
hiring manager early on, et cetera. So I think the stage of company also will dictate, one,

00:35:06.159 --> 00:35:11.199
how formal their system is, two, how many layers you have to go through, and then three, maybe how

00:35:11.199 --> 00:35:17.360
