00:39:15.439 --> 00:39:18.959
actually didn't start from a place where you were really grounded in your own values and what's

00:39:18.959 --> 00:39:23.439
really important to you. So I think that's a great starting point is really thinking about like what

00:39:23.439 --> 00:39:28.159
do you want and what's most important to you in this next step. And then the second piece that I

00:39:28.159 --> 00:39:33.280
really like about this piece of advice is that, and there are many other frameworks, I've heard

00:39:33.280 --> 00:39:37.760
people be like list your top three priorities and three extra criteria, et cetera, et cetera.

00:39:38.320 --> 00:39:43.760
